"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1929074-Rafael-Nadal-Novak-Djokovic-Olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Rafael Nadalwill finally face his biggest rival,Novak Djokovic, more than two years after their last match.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 50, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spaniard defeated Marton Fucsovics 6-1 4-6 6-4. in the first round of the Olympics to set up a highly-anticipated, mouthwatering 60th meeting with the top seed.\", \"from\": 111, \"to\": 275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 111, \"end\": 123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\", \"score\": 0.7999966551257347, \"rank\": 0.2500000000000275, \"text\": \"The Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\"}, {\"begin\": 133, \"end\": 149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\", \"score\": 0.9999999956035026, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marton Fucsovics\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes after Nadalbrushed off claims that it would be his \\\"last dance\\\" with Djokovic, hinting that he is not planning to retire after the Paris 2024 games.\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.662460456503746e-18, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 417, \"end\": 427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.6018046073449897e-13, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were doubts over whether Nadal would even take to the court for his first-round singles match after he joined forces withCarlos Alcarazin the doubles on Saturday night.\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 467, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2929438896470695e-14, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After they won, heblasted the \\\"outrageous\\\" decisionto schedule his clash with Fucsovics second in Sunday's day session.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 38-year-old has also been wearing heavy strapping on his right thigh and cancelled his singles practice on Thursday, only returning on Friday to practice doubles.\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But after another training session on Sunday morning, he decided to remain in the draw and came out to face Fucsovics.\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The King of Clay got off to a blistering start on his favourite court, racing into a 6-1 lead.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But trouble struck early in the second set when Fucsovics broke immediately.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Hungarian struggled to close it out and Nadal pounced, breaking back when Fucsovics served for the set.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1195, \"end\": 1204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_language\", \"score\": 0.8215043823373867, \"rank\": 0.1918397705571722, \"text\": \"Hungarian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2929438896470695e-14, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just in:Novak Djokovic responds to Andy Murray proposition at Olympic Games  Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.349556045547685e-63, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    But the 32-year-old responded by breaking again to force a decider.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1604, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After blowing four break points in two games, Nadal's back was against the wall when he went 0-40 down on his serve.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res